    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Achillea Millefolium Flower/Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower/Foeniculum Vulgare (Fennel) Fruit/Humulus Lupulus (Hops)/Melissa Officinalis Leaf/Viscum Album (Mistletoe) Fruit Extract is the extract of the flowers of Achillea millefolium, Chamomilla recutita; the fruit of Foeniculum vulgare (fennel); the inflorescence (hops cone) of Humulus lupulus; the leaves of Melissa officinalis; and the fruit of Viscum album. The accepted scientific name for Chamomilla recutita is Matricaria chamomilla."
